Facebook group Hashtag I’m Staying has issued a Christmas challenge encouraging people to double their bills so waiters get a 100% tip. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Hundreds of waiters countrywide are sporting smiles, thanks to a new challenge. Facebook group #I’mStaying has issued a Christmas challenge, encouraging people to double their bills so waiters get a 100 percent tip. READ: The restaurant that gets your order wrong (for a good cause) Various posts of people who have accepted this challenge have been shared on the group’s Facebook page. The group was formed in September and has more than a million members. This challenge is not limited to waiters, and people are encouraged to spoil all those who work for tips with a little extra.